      "dependencies": "",
      "description": "This operation removes the input objects from their scope. In case input object is of type <i>Mpr0MfgProcessElement</i>, if the object is released, a new discontinued revision will be created through revise. If the object is the first revision, it will directly be deleted. For any other working revision, the working revision will be deleted and then a new discontinue revision will be created. Similar action will also be applicable for the associated <i>Mpr0ManufacturingElement</i>.<br />In case input object is of type <i>Mpr0BaseOperation</i>, the working revision will be deleted and any old released revisions will be unlinked from the associated process.<br />For any other business object type, the object will be deleted.",
      "exceptionCondition": "",
      "id": "removeObjects#const,std::vector<Teamcenter::BusinessObject>,&",
